<li><a href="/wiki/Seven_Years_in_Tibet" title="Seven Years in Tibet">Seven Years in Tibet</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Lobsang_Rampa" title="Lobsang Rampa">Lobsang Rampa</a></li>
